{% comment %}
  AayuPain™ Official Terms & Conditions Section
{% endcomment %}

<div class="aayu-policy-page-wrapper">
  <div class="page-width page-width--narrow">
    <div class="aayu-policy-header">
      <span class="aayu-policy-badge">LEGAL TERMS</span>
      <h1 class="aayu-policy-title">Terms & Conditions</h1>
      <p class="aayu-policy-date">Last Updated: July 2026 | AyuPain™ Official Store (ayupain.in)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="aayu-policy-content">
      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>Welcome to AyuPain™ Official Store (ayupain.in). By accessing our website and purchasing our Ayurvedic products, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms & Conditions. Please read them carefully before placing an order.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>2. Product Information & Herbal Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>AyuPain™ Pain Relief Oil is a 100% natural, pure Ayurvedic formulation meant for external application only. While our product is crafted using traditional herbal extracts known for relieving joint, muscle, and knee discomfort, individual results may vary based on usage and personal health conditions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>3. Orders, Pricing & Cash on Delivery (COD)</h2>
        <p>All prices listed on ayupain.in are in Indian Rupees (INR) and inclusive of applicable taxes. We offer Cash on Delivery (COD) across eligible pin codes in India. We reserve the right to verify COD orders via phone call or SMS before dispatching.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>4. Shipping & Delivery</h2>
        <p>Orders are dispatched within 24 to 48 hours of confirmation. Delivery typically takes 3 to 7 business days depending on your location. Tracking details will be shared via SMS/Email once shipped.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>All content, branding, logo, product images, graphics, and text on ayupain.in are the exclusive intellectual property of AyuPain™. Unauthorized reproduction or commercial use is strictly prohibited.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aayu-policy-card">
        <h2>6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions regarding our Terms & Conditions, please contact us at:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@ayupain.in">support@ayupain.in</a></li>
          <li><strong>Phone / Helpline:</strong> <a href="tel:8197383570">+91 8197383570</a></li>
          <li><strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://ayupain.in">ayupain.in</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .aayu-policy-page-wrapper {
    padding: 40px 0 70px 0;
    background: #f8faf9;
    font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
  }
  .aayu-policy-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 35px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-badge {
    background: rgba(14, 90, 54, 0.1);
    color: #0e5a36;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    padding: 4px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-title {
    color: #093f25;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 12px 0 6px 0;
  }
  .aayu-policy-date {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  }
  .aayu-policy-card h2 {
    color: #093f25;
    font-size: 19px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #cca43b;
    display: inline-block;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card p {
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0 0 10px 0;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card ul {
    margin: 10px 0 0 20px;
    padding: 0;
    color: #374151;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .aayu-policy-card a {
    color: #0e5a36;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Terms & Conditions",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
